# The User Manual, in order. THIS IS THE ONLY PLACE THE ORDER IS DECLARED.
#
# The chapter files are deliberately not numbered. `07-configuring.md` looks tidy right up
# to the morning you insert a chapter at 04 and rename eleven files, breaking every
# cross-link in the document and every link anyone ever made to it. The sequence is data,
# so it lives in a file, and the build reads it.
#
# Anything under ref/ is GENERATED from the binary. Do not edit those by hand; run
# `cmake --build build --target docs-reference`.

introduction.md

